data.description: Rare find in Delta Township, Grand Ledge Schools. This traditional two story property sits on 2.5 acres and has such country feel, yet close to shopping, restaurants, schools and I69/96. Covered front porch claims a southern exposure and welcomes you in to a stately foyer with 18 ft ceilings and an impressive view of the open staircase. Office is tucked away privately off the foyer and formal dining and kitchen flow easily welcoming you inside. Slider off the informal dining and kitchen area leads to a back deck with gazebo and incredible views of the countryside. From the garage, find storage and a media room or den/study. The family room opposite the kitchen has a raised tile hearth fireplace and access to a mother in law suite complete with kitchen, living quarters, bath and laundry. Second floor has storage, convenient laundry center, 3 generous bedrooms plus the primary bedroom suite which is sure to impress with large walk in closet, bath with tiled corner whirlpool tub flanked by glass enclosed walk in shower, dual vanities and skylight to add natural light. Partially finished basement areas have another bath, family room and other amenities. Last but not least, a 30 x 40ft pole barn gives you the opportunity for storage and projects or hobbies. The 36 panel solar system has Generac battery system in basement of the home.
